<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Beginner_LiveMode_Needs" s="314252">
  <T n="name">0xA6998573<!--String: "Needs"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Needs_1.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:0e510bc12b914501</T>
      <T n="text">0x21C66E43<!--String: "If you want to care for your Sim’s well being (or <i>experiment</i> with it), look no further! \n\nManaging your Sim’s basic <b><font color='#199C2C'>Needs</font></b> allows them to live happy, fruitful lives; however, if they get low, they will experience <b><font color='#199C2C'>negative Emotions</font></b> and might even <b><font color='#199C2C'>die</font></b>!\n\nYou can see the current state of your Sim’s Needs in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Needs panel</font></b>. If you click on a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Need icon</font></b>, your active Sim will try to do something to improve that Need!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Needs_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:0e510bc12b914502</T>
      <T n="text">0x45FB0A08<!--String: "Your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>physical Needs</font></b> are <b><font color='#199C2C'>Bladder</font></b>, <b><font color='#199C2C'>Hunger</font></b>, <b><font color='#199C2C'>Energy</font></b>, and <b><font color='#199C2C'>Hygiene</font></b>. \n\nOwning and using a toilet, a kitchen with a fridge and stove, a bed, and a shower or bath tub will help you take care of your Sim’s physical Needs."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Needs_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:0e510bc12b914503</T>
      <T n="text">0xC4F7EA47<!--String: "Your Sim’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>mental Needs</font></b> are <b><font color='#199C2C'>Fun</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>Social</font></b>. \n\nInteracting with other <b><font color='#199C2C'>Sims</font></b> and using entertainment <b><font color='#199C2C'>Objects</font></b> such as a TV, book case, computer, or instrument are great ways to improve these Needs."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
